Spread the word.Sirf Tum Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 3rd Aug 2023 - Har Pal GeoSirf Tum revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry.
